description:
Two contour maps and three views and cross-section on two pages. Includes text, and outline
   location maps. Two views showing Split Mountin; Sheep Mountain near Grebull; Cross-section
   A-A' Bou khadra. Relief shown by contours and spot height.
title:
Folds. Plunging Anticlinal and Synclinal Mountain-Arid. Dinosaur National Monument,
   Utah. Bou Khadra, Algeria
subject: Geology
relation: David Rumsey Map Collection at Stanford University Libraries
